SENSER:-
Sensors" ke baare mein bataya hai. Sensors ek electronic device hota hai jo kisi physical quantity jaise temperature, pressure, light, 
sound, motion, etc. ko measure karke electrical signals ya digital data ke roop mein generate karta hai.

Is project mein sensors ka use karke hum car accident ki information collect karenge. Hum different sensors ka use kar sakte hain jaise:

GPS sensor: GPS sensor location information provide karta hai, jisse hum car accident ki exact location determine kar sakte hain.

Accelerometer sensor: Accelerometer sensor car ki acceleration aur deceleration ko measure karta hai. Isse hum car ke speed aur 
impact force jaise parameters calculate kar sakte hain.

Gyroscope sensor: Gyroscope sensor car ki orientation aur rotation ko measure karta hai. Isse hum car ke movement ki direction
aur angle jaise parameters calculate kar sakte hain.

Camera sensor: Camera sensor car accident ki visual information provide karta hai, jisse hum car accident ke severity ko determine kar sakte hain.

In sensors ki readings ko collect karne ke baad, hum inka use karke car accident ki information ko analyze kar sakte hain aur phir us information 
ko emergency services ke liye notify kar sakte hain.




